{
  "id": "RAW_6b7e2bb7",
  "title": "当 AI 出海开始拼规模，达人营销也 Agent 化了",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=Mzg3NDkyMTQ5Mw==&mid=2247499395&idx=1&sn=f353c94873acc8fa587bc6ae220102d8",
  "date": "2026-01-27 09:31:00",
  "author": " 有新Newin",
  "siteName": "有新Newin",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;text-align: center;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.4216691068814056\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1366\" style=\"width:100%;\" type=\"block\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"237\" data-imgfileid=\"100015743\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=e1f93ab7&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FwqO5B9doEHcNIeTjk7VwsOia2er1wBeDGgTxicTW8icD6v1coAv0peY6mPGdYpnG7RsHPFfO85nHAdTBvOPqDicZ7w%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.3074074074074074\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-size: var(--articleFontsize);font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;width: 100%;height: auto !important;\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"173\" data-imgfileid=\"100012589\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=05f1e27c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FwqO5B9doEHfpLmI5MibCVKPa7bw396N24gBz2qTSicrwzRYAvvwsU9Agh6QzwKffAxiaf0f67iaicXic0gu39TFeIEsA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></span></p>\n  <p class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-remoteid=\"\" data-asynid=\"\" src=\"\" data-src=\"\" align=\"\" alt=\"\" border=\"\" data-ratio=\"\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"\" aria-label=\"\" aria-braillelabel=\"\" aria-description=\"\" height=\"\" hspace=\"\" ismap opacity=\"\" sizes=\"\" title=\"\" type=\"block\" usemap=\"\" vspace=\"\" width=\"\" data-width=\"\" data-height=\"\" data-croporisrc=\"\" data-cropx1=\"\" data-cropx2=\"\" data-cropy1=\"\" data-cropy2=\"\" data-cropselx1=\"\" data-cropselx2=\"\" data-cropsely1=\"\" data-cropsely2=\"\" data-backw=\"\" data-backh=\"\" data-copyright=\"\" data-oversubscription-url=\"\" data-before-oversubscription-url=\"\" data-galleryid=\"\" data-gallerysupplier=\"\" data-cardimg=\"\" data-fileid=\"\" data-imgfileid=\"100015464\" data-positionback=\"\" data-imgqrcoded=\"\" data-imgid=\"\" data-upload=\"\" data-fromlib=\"\" data-aiimageid=\"\" data-cacheurl=\"\" data-retry=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" data-aiimagesource=\"\" nodeleaf=\"\"><mp-common-profile class=\"custom_select_card mp_profile_iframe\" data-pluginname=\"mpprofile\" data-nickname=\"有新Newin\" data-alias=\"NewinData\" data-from=\"0\" data-headimg=\"http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/wqO5B9doEHfWpviblkX0cCTHkGRJYxSBgwSqgeKicI9Qm9jOia9oQ19BsiblkJBYDAsu0moqoJrZ8xCC5oWyDjoViaQ/0?wx_fmt=png\" data-signature=\"探索新科技，聚焦新价值。\" data-id=\"Mzg3NDkyMTQ5Mw==\" data-service_type=\"1\" data-verify_status=\"2\"></mp-common-profile></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\">对出海的 AI 科技公司来说，一个越来越清晰且棘手的现实 —— 模型、工具和基础能力的成熟，使得</span></span><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\">产品上线更快、试错成本更低，同类产品迅速增多，而用户的注意力和信任反而变得更加稀缺</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\">。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\">在这样的环境下，营销不只是“把声音放大”的作用，而是需要</span></span><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\">不断通过真实场景，帮助用户理解差异、建立信任、形成付费决策</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\">。达人营销也因此被越来越多出海 AI 公司纳入常态化预算，成为一项长期、持续推进的工作，而不再是一次性的投放尝试。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\">一个很典型的例子是 Canva</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\">。在早期阶段，Canva 的增长高度依赖少量头部创作者，一条讲清楚核心用法的教程视频，就可能在短时间内带来明显的下载和注册增长。但当产品变得更成熟、更大众化之后，这种单点爆发的效果开始明显变弱，内容形式被快速复制，用户的注意力被更高密度的信息迅速稀释。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6565809379727685\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1322\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-width=\"1322\" data-height=\"868\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"369\" data-imgfileid=\"100015734\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=bf37440c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FwqO5B9doEHcNIeTjk7VwsOia2er1wBeDGlMod3oJqL7N2hhicl3Wac4IH03HR3EaJtP2hEgzLnjWcpycsXcwx44g%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\">最早的拐点，大致出现在 2019～2020 年。Canva 的用户规模已经跨过数千万级，产品形态趋于稳定，模板、协作、品牌套件等核心能力成熟，这个阶段&nbsp;</span></span><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\">“靠少数设计博主做爆款内容” 已经无法支撑增长效率</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\">。团队开始意识到，真正驱动使用频率和留存的，是大量具体、细分、可复制的使用场景被持续演示出来。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5758998435054773\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"639\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-width=\"639\" data-height=\"368\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"324\" data-imgfileid=\"100015732\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=02c2ed89&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FwqO5B9doEHcNIeTjk7VwsOia2er1wBeDG3gPuxTj6miaJe95YfTNiaoDibKWrjPDQKR4GkVtZEGztyau2pt840Nw8Q%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\">Canva 意识到一个变化：</span></span><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\">当产品进入规模阶段，达人营销的重点已经不在于追逐少量爆款，而在于保持稳定的内容密度；</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\">2020～2021 年，Canva 明显强化了 Creator 体系和 Ambassador 体系，从明星级达人，到覆盖不同国家、语言、职业角色的中腰部创作者，包括教师、HR、创业者、跨境卖家、内容创作者等细分人群。</span></span></p>\n  <h2 style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:18px;\">▍</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:18px;\">规模化，正在变成一种竞争形态</span></span></h2>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\">A16Z 合伙人 Andrew Chen 提出的“Cold Start Theory”解释了网络型产品是如何从“没人用”走到“自增长”的：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.511875\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1600\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-width=\"1600\" data-height=\"819\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"288\" data-imgfileid=\"100015733\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=ecfe3ce2&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FwqO5B9doEHcNIeTjk7VwsOia2er1wBeDGibEXn9aojgvxjc2cPs4op3EnU2jYPXngSFFsn6yG45URTIYTFNegmsg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\">当产品逐渐走出冷启动阶段，真正重要的变化是</span></span><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\">某些使用场景开始变得“可被反复看见”，一旦这种密度在更多细分场景中被复制，增长就会进入自驱阶段，竞争焦点也从早期 PMF 阶段迈向规模化营销</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\">。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\">对 AI、科技类出海产品而言，这种变化来得尤为直接。随着产品能力本身逐渐同质化，达人营销已经很难依靠一次性的 Campaign 完成用户教育。</span></span><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\">在信息流持续被算法切碎的环境中，用户的记忆周期不断缩短，注意力成本持续上升，品牌只有长期、稳定、高频地出现在真实使用场景中，才有可能被真正记住</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\">。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\">规模化这一步，最容易被误解是仍然用 “达人量级” 去理解内容效果。</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\">在投放早期，很多团队会自然偏向头部达人，认为粉丝量直接等于播放量和转化能力；也有一些团队走向另一个极端，只投小博主，希望用更低成本“赌效率”。但问题的关键并不在于“选哪一类达人”，而在于</span></span><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\">内容是否跑出了足够密集的使用场景 ——&nbsp;</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\">真正稳定有效的结果，往往是建立在 UGC 密度之上的。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\">原因并不复杂：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\">首先，在 Instagram、TikTok 这类算法平台上，播放量早已不再由粉丝数直接决定。真正影响分发的，是用户在前几秒的停留、互动和观看行为。随着平台对 UGC 内容依赖加深，粉丝量在分发中的权重持续被削弱。算法更关心的是：这条内容被推给同类用户时，</span></span><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\">他们会不会愿意继续看下去</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\">。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\">其次，在 AI 这种高度个性化的产品领域，受众本身就极其分散，并不依赖某一种固定的人设或权威背书。这也意味着，AI 产品天然不适合单一叙事。 UGC 的价值，早已不只是“真实”“便宜”“自然”，而是在今天逐渐演化为品牌的外脑</span></span><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\">：</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\">不断为产品创造新的使用方式和理解路径。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\">同一个产品，一旦进入不同创作者的语境，使用方式就会迅速分化。</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\">创作者会结合自己的职业背景、创作习惯和受众结构，重新定义产品的使用场景。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\">以 AI 生图为例：</span></span></p>\n  <ul class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\">在电商设计类创作者手中，它更多被用于商品主图、详情页和视觉优化；</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\">在 3D 建模相关内容中，它承担的是概念建模和草图迭代；</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\">而在品牌设计师的视角下，又会自然延展到品牌 KV、宣传物料，甚至整套视觉系统的生成。</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\">这些内容彼此并不冲突，却共同构成了一张完整的产品使用版图。这些不同使用方式在不同平台反复出现后，逐渐形成的一整套</span></span><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\">可理解、可代入的使用场景集合，</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\">这正是 AI 产品心智建立的必经之路。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\">那些长期跑得最稳的品牌，本质上优先搭建起了一个</span></span><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\">足够密集、足够多样的 UGC 内容网络。在这个网络中，小体量的达人成为场景生成的主体，头部达人承担的是放大与心智强化的功能。</span></span></strong></p>\n  <h2 style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:18px;\">▍</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:18px;\">规模上来后，问题不再是“更努力”</span></span></h2>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\">该如何链接足量的达人呢？</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\">这也是很多出海团队撞上的现实问题 ——&nbsp;</span></span><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\">每个月要落地上百位达人的内容落地，仅靠人力，是不可持续的。</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\">无论是 in-house 扩编，还是把执行外包出去，问题并不会消失，只是从一个角色转移到另一个角色。执行压力、沟通成本和复杂度，始终存在，而且只会随着规模放大而被不断放大。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.34267413931144913\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"2498\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-width=\"2498\" data-height=\"856\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"193\" data-imgfileid=\"100015735\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=f9340e12&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FwqO5B9doEHcNIeTjk7VwsOia2er1wBeDGlALOd9xMTLXVLaibYQ5fn2P4I1l9MggGHcDtazOK1Kqk0nt5TG8UsWA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\">Aha 的切入点是把那些在达人营销中每天大量消耗精力、却并不依赖创造性决策的执行事务，逐步沉淀为一套可以长期、稳定运转的平台化工作流。这些能力也是在达人营销专家多年实战经验的基础上，伴随着真实项目不断被拆解、验证和修正，才逐步形成的。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6234247590808006\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"2698\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-width=\"2698\" data-height=\"1682\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"350\" data-imgfileid=\"100015736\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=b05a63cc&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FwqO5B9doEHcNIeTjk7VwsOia2er1wBeDGTuhjc9vreH4CiaOMZoM5icUKX18SGy5AnmV8mBUc7slw5noYpZ8icZKWw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\">从 Campaign 发起开始，达人匹配、合作推进、内容交付都在同一套流程中完成，合作不再依赖临时沟通或个人经验，而是基于结构化信息持续扩展可建联合作的达人池，能同时支撑大量 UGC与不同量级的创作者合作，客户只需要把产品信息、目标市场和合作预期写清楚，剩下最重、最耗时的执行工作，都可以交给 AI 员工去跑。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\">比如找达人这件事。过去大家都很熟：先圈人、再私信、等回复、反复谈价，效率极不稳定。现在的变化在于，AI 会根据 Campaign 需求，直接从一个&nbsp;</span></span><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\">500 万 + 的全球严选达人池</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\">里帮你找到最适合的达人，这些达人</span></span><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\">覆盖 AI 生产提效类、AI 测评类、设计工具、开发工具等多个内容方向，分布在主流内容平台和 140+ 个国家和地区。</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.47173489278752434\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"2052\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-width=\"2052\" data-height=\"968\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"265\" data-imgfileid=\"100015737\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=fd572d11&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FwqO5B9doEHcNIeTjk7VwsOia2er1wBeDGutCQTAOMODktHcrCmsb4wAB0Ezo38JmycAqXRS4JyicE9bYWMq1xl7Q%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\">在实际执行中，你拿到的不是一份“待沟通名单”，而是一份</span></span><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\">已经完成建联、价格清晰的、可以立即推进内容制作的备选清单。选中，达人就能立即推进内容制作。</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\">这套结构也能支撑起了品牌真正有价值的规模化诉求：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\">在月度合作中，达人结构会自然分布在：头部（约 20%）、腰部（约 30%）和长尾（约 50%）。既能保证必要的放大效应，又能通过大量 UGC 持续生成多样化的使用场景，让品牌在一个周期内同时落地上百位达人的合作成为常态。</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-backh=\"348\" data-backw=\"562\" data-height=\"1674\" data-imgfileid=\"100015740\" data-ratio=\"0.62\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"2700\" data-width=\"2700\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=f33f20d6&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FwqO5B9doEHcNIeTjk7VwsOia2er1wBeDGU0fvsicZg9ScWlV3FS4SxXIb8pEKYzGEUWLgGVKp70mhibIBnibMnuaPA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\">这种变化带来的体感非常明显。你不再需要每天盯着私信回复，也不需要反复纠结“这个价格是不是被抬高了”。最消耗心力的沟通和议价已经被 AI 前置完成，你只需要做一件事：</span></span><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\">判断要不要合作</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\">。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-backh=\"333\" data-backw=\"562\" data-imgfileid=\"100015746\" data-ratio=\"0.59296875\" data-s=\"300,640\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1280\" style=\"width:100%;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=a7b02c54&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FwqO5B9doEHcNIeTjk7VwsOia2er1wBeDGS3cUatgfQsjWVy4TfHic3k8O4yW3hQgD9jpFgPCMjqHX8J2NhxFabsg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\">当达人进入制作阶段后，另一个长期困扰团队的问题也开始被系统性解决：催稿。在 Aha 平台中，达人是否按期提交、是否延期、是否进入二稿制作，都会由AI员工在背后充当“监工”角色，根据实际进展中的达人情况，在平台按不同节点（待审核、内容制作中、内容待发布、已发布） “整理” 并持续跟进。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\">一旦节点发生变化，比如逾期，AI 会像一个执行同事一样反复提醒，直到节点完成。整个过程中，团队不需要频繁介入，也不会因为某一次遗漏、疏忽拖慢该达人的整体节奏。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\">规模化之所以能成立，除了效率之外，还有保障。</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\">随着合作量放大，风险和资金问题也会被同步放大。很多团队都是在“出过一次问题之后”，才意识到这件事的严重性：内容未按约定交付、发布时间被反复拖延、使用权边界模糊，甚至在结算环节出现纠纷，最终既消耗精力，也影响合作关系。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-backh=\"233\" data-backw=\"562\" data-height=\"1036\" data-imgfileid=\"100015739\" data-ratio=\"0.41373801916932906\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"2504\" data-width=\"2504\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=b30a6559&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FwqO5B9doEHcNIeTjk7VwsOia2er1wBeDGnKlgGjLtqr3HpWF8AyKevax0kg0Aqvvx5IYicb25Ry0TJH2lok8TFxQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\">Aha 的做法是，</span></span><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\">把履约和资金安全直接写进执行流程里</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\">：在合作开始之前，达人身份、内容授权范围和使用规范就会被统一校验，避免在内容发布后再反复确认权责；预算由平台进行托管，只有在内容按约定完成并通过验收后，才会进入结算流程，从机制上降低履约和资金风险。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\">这背后显露出一个缓慢但确定性的趋势 —— 达人营销开始从过往消耗人力的任务转变为平台性的工作流，执行已经被交付给 AI 员工，企业不再需要被日常执行细节不断拉走注意力，而是可以把精力重新放回到业务效果以及关键决策。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\">这也构成了 Aha 与传统 in-house 或 Agency 的本质差异。后者更多是在替你补充人力，而 Aha 关注的是：在规模化达人合作中，“干好活”“做好保障”，从推进、履约、审稿到结算，都不再依赖个人盯控。</span></span></p>\n  <h2 style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:18px;\">▍</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:18px;\">真正拉开差距的，是执行模式</span></span></h2>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\">我们发现，Aha 服务的 AI 科技客户中</span></span><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\">占比最高、使用效果也最稳定的一类，是单月达人营销预算在 $100k 美金以上的团队</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\">。这里面既有</span></span><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\">阿里巴巴</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\">这样的成熟组织，也包括一些比较知名的 AI 出海产品，比如&nbsp;</span></span><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\">AiPPT</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\">、</span></span><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\">Vizard、Zeemo 等</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\">。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.40667196187450355\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"2518\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-width=\"2518\" data-height=\"1024\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"229\" data-imgfileid=\"100015741\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=60796df7&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FwqO5B9doEHcNIeTjk7VwsOia2er1wBeDGjQ0D4x0BWJPlicHtSyEuOrppd9b2BicZ6HiaWtj0RGBFNdlBoDu5sibyicg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\">当达人营销进入“稳定、持续在跑”的状态，很多企业都转变了自己的执行模式。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\">以 Autocoder 为例，这是一款面向非程序员的 AI 应用生成工具。早期在小规模测试中，团队很快确认：达人营销的整体效果明显优于广告投放，这条路径值得继续放大。但随着合作频率提高，问题也随之显现——达人供给难以持续、沟通链路冗长、内容和履约节奏难以稳定。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\">在当时的执行结构下，即便预算充足，每一轮合作仍然需要反复从找人、建联、谈价开始。达人数量一旦增加，节奏就不可避免地被拉慢，增长团队需要花大量时间在跟进和协调上，而不是判断内容是否有效。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\">真正的变化发生在执行模式的调整。Autocoder 团队第一次用 Aha，是通过业内朋友推荐。使用后的感受并不复杂：</span></span><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\">过去需要反复切换邮箱、私信、表格的流程，被收进了一个统一的节奏里</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\">。找人、建联、谈价、付款和内容交付在平台内自动推进，团队只需要做判断——这个达人值不值得合作。增长同学反馈，在平台上筛一个达人大约&nbsp;</span></span><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\">2 分钟</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\">，每天&nbsp;</span></span><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\">1～2 小时</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\">，就能推进整条达人营销链路，</span></span><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\">整体效率提升 80% 以上</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\">。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\">结果也非常具体：合作交付的</span></span><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\">达人数量达到百位规模</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\">仍能持续推进，短视频上线周期缩短到&nbsp;</span></span><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\">1 周左右</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\">，而此前通过 Agency 往往需要&nbsp;</span></span><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\">3 周</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\">；注册成本至少下降&nbsp;</span></span><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\">50%</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\">，大多数达人报价落在团队预期区间内，内容表现也更加稳定。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\">把视角放得更远一点，会发现这些调整并不是孤立发生的。</span></span><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\">AI 产品的全球化，正在把增长节奏整体推快</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\">：市场更多、语言更多、内容形态更多，留给单次判断和人工协调的时间却越来越少。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\">在这种背景下，达人营销不再只是一个内容问题，而变成了能否在不同市场稳定复制执行能力的问题</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\">。能够持续跑下去的，往往是那些</span></span><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\">更早把执行交给平台，把人力留给判断和方向的团队，这正是 AI 出海进入深水区之后，一种正在浮现的共同行为模式。</span></span></strong></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "本文探讨了 AI 出海背景下达人营销的规模化趋势，并重点介绍了 Aha 平台如何通过 Agent 化工作流解决全球营销中的执行效率与履约保障问题。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "本文探讨了 AI 出海背景下达人营销的规模化趋势，并重点介绍了 Aha 平台如何通过 Agent 化工作流解决全球营销中的执行效率与履约保障问题。",
  "summary": "文章分析了 AI 出海产品面临的同质化竞争与用户注意力稀缺现状，指出达人营销已从早期的“单点爆款”转向“高密度场景覆盖”的规模化阶段。以 Canva 为例，说明了建立多层次创作者体系对驱动增长的重要性。针对大规模营销中面临的找人难、沟通累、履约险等痛点，文章推介了 Aha 平台。该平台利用 AI Agent 自动化处理达人匹配、建联、议价、催稿及结算等繁琐执行环节，将传统人力驱动的营销任务转变为标准化的平台工作流。通过 Autocoder 等实战案例证明，这种 Agent 化的执行模式能显著提升效率、降低获客成本，是 AI 企业应对全球化快速增长节奏的关键手段。",
